tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE shipment_schedule (
    shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    shipment_code VARCHAR(255),
    source_location VARCHAR(255),
    destination_location VARCHAR(255),
    estimated_arrival_time TIMESTAMP,
    actual_arrival_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE shipment_schedule (
 shipment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 arrival_time TIMESTAMP,
 departure_time TIMESTAMP,
 pickup_location TEXT,
 delivery_location TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE delivery_timeline (
 timeline_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 shipment_id UUID,
 scheduled_delivery_time TIMESTAMP,
 actual_delivery_time TIMESTAMP,
 delivery_status TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE shipment_schedule (
  shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  shipment_date DATE NOT NULL,
  estimated_delivery_date DATE,
  current_status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE delivery_timeline (
  timeline_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  shipment_id INT NOT NULL,
  event_description TEXT,
  event_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE cross_docking_logistics (
  logistics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  shipment_id INT NOT NULL,
  dock_location VARCHAR(50),
  estimated_processing_time INT
)

CREATE TABLE shipment_schedule (
    shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    shipment_date DATE,
    arrival_time TIME,
    departure_time TIME,
    from_location VARCHAR(255),
    to_location VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE delivery_timeline (
    delivery_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    delivery_date DATE,
    delivery_time TIME,
    status VARCHAR(50),
    notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE logistics_company (
    company_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_person VARCHAR(100),
    contact_email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);
